item.title: Is there a way to unlock all music tracks on 718?
item.dc:creator: @rastanoob2 rastanoob2
item.description:
@rastanoob2 wrote:

[quote=“Potzon, post:2, topic:477985”]Open MusicsManager.java, and replace your MusicsManager method with this one:

public MusicsManager() { unlockedMusics = new ArrayList<Integer>(); playList = new ArrayList<Integer>(12); // auto unlock all musics - pixel for (int i = 0; i < 1200; i++) unlockedMusics.add(i); }

Tell me if you get any errors.[/quote]

Thanks alot, it worked, no errors

item.title: Is there a way to unlock all music tracks on 718?
item.dc:creator: @Potzon Potzon
item.description:
@Potzon wrote:

Open MusicsManager.java, and replace your MusicsManager method with this one:

public MusicsManager() { unlockedMusics = new ArrayList<Integer>(); playList = new ArrayList<Integer>(12); // auto unlock all musics - pixel for (int i = 0; i < 1200; i++) unlockedMusics.add(i); }

Tell me if you get any errors.
